### 회원가입
@name getToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "nickname": "tester",
    "password": "password"
}

### 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "password": "password"
}

### 로그아웃
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/logout
Cookie: {{accessTokenName}}={{accessToken}}


### 상품 등록
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Cookie: {{accessTokenName}}={{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"Test_Product",
    "description":"Test_Description",
    "price":10000,
    "tags":["test_tag"]
}

### 상품 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1
Cookie: {{accessTokenName}}={{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name":"Updated_Test_Product"
}

### 상품 덧글 작성
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/comments/2
Cookie: {{accessTokenName}}={{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

